title: recently remodeled Ranch`Newer Appliances` new toilet and tub @@
posting_body: This recently remodeled Ranch has a lot to offer!!
(3) Generous Bedrooms, a Huge Living Room, Eat-In Kitchen with Newer Appliances, AND a Formal Dining Area await your Enjoyment!
The whole house was painted, with new flooring in the kitchen and bathroom, a new toilet and tub in the bathroom, a newer kitchen sink, and a New 100amp Siemens Electrical Panel.
Ohio State Waterproofing has kept this lower-level DRY since the day it was installed!
No damp or mildew odors in this Home!
There's also a Newer Tear-Off Roof installed in 2016 along with New Gutters and Downspouts!
Last but not least the current owner also installed NEW entry and storm doors.
